The Cool Carat Seat Cooler is your ideal accessory to take on the summer heat. This Seat Cooler is easily placed onto your child‚Äö√Ñ√¥s car seat to cool it down.

The Car Seat Cooler from Cool Carats is great for running errands and protecting your little one's car seat when the car is left in the sun. Simply place the cooler in the freezer and use it when required. With a patented Cooltech design, this liner will keep your little one's seat cool for up to 8 hours, perfect for the hot Australian Sun keeping your little one safe. The cooler is designed to be used when the seat is unoccupied and should be removed when placing your child in the car.
